room_title: Escape room "TAKEN BY ALIENS" by Disaster Room 915 in El Paso
room_description: Aliens have come to Earth! Their spaceship is here! You're interested so of course you go to get a closer look...when before you know it, you've been abducted! Can you make it off the ship before it takes off? Or will you live the rest of your life as an Alien guinea pig?
